      "citation_id": "[CITATION_1]",
      "span_text": "Suitable mineral standards including anorthoclase, basaltic glass, chromite, chromium augite, diopside, ilmenite, microcline, and plagioclase, all certified by the United States National Museum as reference samples for electron microprobe analysis [CITATION_1] were applied to calculate mineral and melt compositions."
    }
